OL,7,FThe Institute for Fiscal Studies (IFS)
OL,8,Fsays that if Rachel Reeves wishes not
OL,9,Fonly to alleviate the pressure on
OL,10,Fschools, hospitals, prisons, courts
OL,11,Fand local authorities but also to
OL,12,Fimprove the services they offer, then
OL,13,Fshe may need to raise up to #25
OL,14,Fbillion a year from tax increases in
OL,15,Fher Budget on October 30.
