OL,3,CUp to #25 billion in tax rises may be
OL,4,Cneeded for 'no return to austerity'
OL,5,Cpledge
OL,7,FIn the last few weeks, the chancellor
OL,8,Fhas spoken often about the need to
OL,9,Fraise investment to lift economic
OL,10,Fgrowth and we already know that she
OL,11,Fplans to change the debt rule she
OL,12,Finherited from the Conservatives in
OL,13,Forder to do this.
OL,15,FBut the IFS warns doing this will do
OL,16,F"almost nothing" to improve funding
OL,17,Ffor public services.
