OL,7,FIn the IFS's view, this means she
OL,8,Fwould almost certainly need to turn to
OL,9,Ftax rises rather than borrowing if she
OL,10,Fwished to avoid cuts to some
OL,11,Fdepartmental budgets.
OL,13,FThe director of the IFS, Paul Johnson,
OL,14,Fsays the Budget on October 30 could
OL,15,Fprove to be "the most consequential
OL,16,Fsince at least 2010".
