OL,7,FThe IFS points out that were the
OL,8,Fgovernment to raise taxes by a total
OL,9,Fof #25 billion in three weeks time,
OL,10,Fthe increase would be larger than
OL,11,Fthose announced by Gordon Brown in his
OL,12,Ffirst budget in July 1997 and by
OL,13,FGeorge Osborne in October 2010 (both
OL,14,Faround #13 billion).
